@bongfranc @daemoonyo Hi, Bong. The One Health Pass must be filled out by all incoming travelers to the Philippines. To register, please click this link: https://t.co/VvpaX0DMPM.

All information shared in the One Health Pass is collected and processed solely by the Bureau of Quarantine (BOQ). 

